\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:52:30.000Z","msg":"唔係傳聞嚟咋咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"前AV女優紅音螢 (紅音ほたるが) 有「潮吹女王」之稱，引退後投身宣導正確性知識活動，為年輕人解決性方面的困擾。但紅音螢的同居男子指出，紅音螢某天在返家休息過程中，突然身體不適、四肢僵硬躺床上而暴斃，目前警方仍在調查。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de1ff51be9187d8e5231f2f3800faea71ea6ce4","tid":1077943,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d29d506b3673b1abbd7d76c809326882ac60c97","tid":1077943,"uid":62837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"麻美由真 來生光都冇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"麻美世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d69f63590a1d32f48f5bb78d5ae88a73487bd5","tid":1077943,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"小蕾？"},{"pid":"8a39047596358b467de175e487f4d7384efc5555","tid":1077943,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"蒼井空到底係咩人捧起<br />\n講av先驅又唔到佢<br />\n講正又唔到佢<br />\n把老牛聲一叫起上嚟直頭係嘈"}]}